that time. That time was part of his life. And I just

07:20.381 --> 07:24.486
have never lived books like Bill did. And so he 
worked for us for, I forget how long it was, five or

07:32.078 --> 07:34.461
six years. And one day, I was riding with him on a 
trip, and I said, where do you want to go? What do you

07:44.156 --> 07:46.118
